source.name: List of Nuclear Materials Licensing Actions Received
source.description: A catalog of all Materials Licensing Actions received for review.  The catalog lists the name of the entity submitting the license application, their city and state, the license number, the docket number, the NRC Region that handled the review, and the type of license application involved.
